{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":934,"text":"The day I left home for the first time"},{"time":2791,"text":"to go to university was a bright day"},{"time":4971,"text":"brimming with hope and optimism."},{"time":7516,"text":"I'd done well at school.\nExpectations for me were high,"},{"time":10463,"text":"and I gleefully entered the student life"},{"time":12638,"text":"of lectures, parties\nand traffic cone theft."},{"time":16236,"text":"Now appearances, of course,\ncan be deceptive,"},{"time":18914,"text":"and to an extent, this\nfeisty, energetic persona"},{"time":22029,"text":"of lecture-going and traffic\ncone stealing was a veneer,"},{"time":25184,"text":"albeit a very well-crafted\nand convincing one."},{"time":28223,"text":"Underneath, I was actually\ndeeply unhappy, insecure"},{"time":31649,"text":"and fundamentally frightened --"},{"time":33863,"text":"frightened of other people,\nof the future, of failure"},{"time":37486,"text":"and of the emptiness\nthat I felt was within me."},{"time":39839,"text":"But I was skilled at hiding\nit, and from the outside"},{"time":42340,"text":"appeared to be someone\nwith everything to hope for"},{"time":44745,"text":"and aspire to."},{"time":45996,"text":"This fantasy of invulnerability\nwas so complete"},{"time":49202,"text":"that I even deceived myself,"},{"time":50914,"text":"and as the first semester\nended and the second began,"},{"time":53462,"text":"there was no way that anyone\ncould have predicted"},{"time":55994,"text":"what was just about to happen."},{"time":58617,"text":"I was leaving a seminar when it started,"},{"time":61750,"text":"humming to myself, fumbling with my bag"},{"time":63911,"text":"just as I'd done a hundred times before,"},{"time":66334,"text":"when suddenly I heard\na voice calmly observe,"},{"time":68810,"text":"\"She is leaving the room.\""},{"time":71002,"text":"I looked around, and there\nwas no one there,"},{"time":72417,"text":"but the clarity\nand decisiveness of the comment"},{"time":75091,"text":"was unmistakable."},{"time":76935,"text":"Shaken, I left my books\non the stairs and hurried home,"},{"time":79579,"text":"and there it was again."},{"time":80818,"text":"\"She is opening the door.\""},{"time":82881,"text":"This was the beginning.\nThe voice had arrived."},{"time":86853,"text":"And the voice persisted,"},{"time":89100,"text":"days and then weeks of it, on and on,"},{"time":91565,"text":"narrating everything I did\nin the third person."},{"time":93828,"text":"\"She is going to the library.\""},{"time":95486,"text":"\"She is going to a lecture.\""},{"time":97081,"text":"It was neutral, impassive\nand even, after a while,"},{"time":100417,"text":"strangely companionate and reassuring,"},{"time":102999,"text":"although I did notice that its\ncalm exterior sometimes slipped"},{"time":106440,"text":"and that it occasionally mirrored\nmy own unexpressed emotion."},{"time":109541,"text":"So, for example, if I was angry\nand had to hide it,"},{"time":112153,"text":"which I often did, being very adept\nat concealing how I really felt,"},{"time":115519,"text":"then the voice would sound frustrated."},{"time":117856,"text":"Otherwise, it was neither\nsinister nor disturbing,"},{"time":120669,"text":"although even at that point it was clear"},{"time":122779,"text":"that it had something to communicate to me"},{"time":124803,"text":"about my emotions, particularly emotions"},{"time":127174,"text":"which were remote and inaccessible."},{"time":130259,"text":"Now it was then that I made\na fatal mistake,"},{"time":133383,"text":"in that I told a friend\nabout the voice, and she was horrified."},{"time":136586,"text":"A subtle conditioning process had begun,"},{"time":138831,"text":"the implication that normal\npeople don't hear voices"},{"time":142520,"text":"and the fact that I did meant\nthat something was very seriously wrong."},{"time":145878,"text":"Such fear and mistrust was infectious."},{"time":149266,"text":"Suddenly the voice didn't\nseem quite so benign anymore,"},{"time":152331,"text":"and when she insisted\nthat I seek medical attention,"},{"time":154832,"text":"I duly complied, and which proved to be"},{"time":156903,"text":"mistake number two."},{"time":158650,"text":"I spent some time telling the college G.P."},{"time":160796,"text":"about what I perceived\nto be the real problem:"},{"time":163011,"text":"anxiety, low self-worth,\nfears about the future,"},{"time":165867,"text":"and was met with bored indifference"},{"time":167640,"text":"until I mentioned the voice,"},{"time":169434,"text":"upon which he dropped his pen, swung round"},{"time":171458,"text":"and began to question me\nwith a show of real interest."},{"time":174169,"text":"And to be fair, I was desperate\nfor interest and help,"},{"time":176813,"text":"and I began to tell him\nabout my strange commentator."},{"time":179659,"text":"And I always wish, at this\npoint, the voice had said,"},{"time":182207,"text":"\"She is digging her own grave.\""},{"time":183899,"text":"I was referred\nto a psychiatrist, who likewise"},{"time":187424,"text":"took a grim view of the voice's presence,"},{"time":189981,"text":"subsequently interpreting\neverything I said"},{"time":192053,"text":"through a lens of latent insanity."},{"time":194389,"text":"For example, I was part\nof a student TV station"},{"time":197322,"text":"that broadcast news bulletins\naround the campus,"},{"time":199874,"text":"and during an appointment\nwhich was running very late,"},{"time":201924,"text":"I said, \"I'm sorry,\ndoctor, I've got to go."},{"time":203173,"text":"I'm reading the news at six.\""},{"time":204691,"text":"Now it's down on my medical\nrecords that Eleanor"},{"time":207001,"text":"has delusions that she's a television\nnews broadcaster."},{"time":210175,"text":"It was at this point that events began"},{"time":213624,"text":"to rapidly overtake me."},{"time":215854,"text":"A hospital admission\nfollowed, the first of many,"},{"time":218250,"text":"a diagnosis of schizophrenia came next,"},{"time":221162,"text":"and then, worst of all,\na toxic, tormenting sense"},{"time":224770,"text":"of hopelessness, humiliation and despair"},{"time":228148,"text":"about myself and my prospects."},{"time":230683,"text":"But having been encouraged\nto see the voice"},{"time":233116,"text":"not as an experience but as a symptom,"},{"time":235672,"text":"my fear and resistance\ntowards it intensified."},{"time":238768,"text":"Now essentially, this represented taking"},{"time":240852,"text":"an aggressive stance towards my own mind,"},{"time":242904,"text":"a kind of psychic civil war,"},{"time":245295,"text":"and in turn this caused\nthe number of voices to increase"},{"time":248229,"text":"and grow progressively\nhostile and menacing."},{"time":251614,"text":"Helplessly and hopelessly,\nI began to retreat"},{"time":255094,"text":"into this nightmarish inner world"},{"time":257233,"text":"in which the voices\nwere destined to become"},{"time":259305,"text":"both my persecutors\nand my only perceived companions."},{"time":263327,"text":"They told me, for example,\nthat if I proved myself worthy"},{"time":266406,"text":"of their help, then\nthey could change my life"},{"time":268573,"text":"back to how it had been,"},{"time":269770,"text":"and a series of increasingly\nbizarre tasks was set,"},{"time":272510,"text":"a kind of labor of Hercules."},{"time":274535,"text":"It started off quite small, for example,"},{"time":276496,"text":"pull out three strands of hair,"},{"time":278212,"text":"but gradually it grew more extreme,"},{"time":279903,"text":"culminating in commands to harm myself,"},{"time":282123,"text":"and a particularly dramatic instruction:"},{"time":284293,"text":"\"You see that tutor over there?"},{"time":286006,"text":"You see that glass of water?"},{"time":287304,"text":"Well, you have to go over and pour it\nover him in front of the other students.\""},{"time":290102,"text":"Which I actually did,\nand which needless to say"},{"time":292365,"text":"did not endear me to the faculty."},{"time":294046,"text":"In effect, a vicious cycle\nof fear, avoidance,"},{"time":298350,"text":"mistrust and misunderstanding\nhad been established,"},{"time":301208,"text":"and this was a battle\nin which I felt powerless"},{"time":303960,"text":"and incapable of establishing\nany kind of peace or reconciliation."},{"time":308337,"text":"Two years later,\nand the deterioration was dramatic."},{"time":311995,"text":"By now, I had the whole\nfrenzied repertoire:"},{"time":315703,"text":"terrifying voices, grotesque visions,"},{"time":318692,"text":"bizarre, intractable delusions."},{"time":321460,"text":"My mental health status\nhad been a catalyst"},{"time":323656,"text":"for discrimination, verbal abuse,"},{"time":326245,"text":"and physical and sexual assault,"},{"time":328400,"text":"and I'd been told by my psychiatrist,"},{"time":330186,"text":"\"Eleanor, you'd be better off with cancer,"},{"time":332595,"text":"because cancer is easier\nto cure than schizophrenia.\""},{"time":336348,"text":"I'd been diagnosed, drugged and discarded,"},{"time":339740,"text":"and was by now so tormented by the voices"},{"time":341816,"text":"that I attempted to drill\na hole in my head"},{"time":344021,"text":"in order to get them out."},{"time":346877,"text":"Now looking back on the wreckage\nand despair of those years,"},{"time":350978,"text":"it seems to me now as if someone\ndied in that place,"},{"time":354048,"text":"and yet, someone else was saved."},{"time":357765,"text":"A broken and haunted\nperson began that journey,"},{"time":361079,"text":"but the person who emerged was a survivor"},{"time":364012,"text":"and would ultimately grow into the person"},{"time":366286,"text":"I was destined to be."},{"time":368410,"text":"Many people have harmed me in my life,"},{"time":371098,"text":"and I remember them all,"},{"time":372592,"text":"but the memories grow pale and faint"},{"time":375393,"text":"in comparison with the people\nwho've helped me."},{"time":379085,"text":"The fellow survivors,\nthe fellow voice-hearers,"},{"time":381705,"text":"the comrades and collaborators;"},{"time":383977,"text":"the mother who never gave up on me,"},{"time":386305,"text":"who knew that one day\nI would come back to her"},{"time":388913,"text":"and was willing to wait for me\nfor as long as it took;"},{"time":392583,"text":"the doctor who only worked\nwith me for a brief time"},{"time":395120,"text":"but who reinforced\nhis belief that recovery"},{"time":397192,"text":"was not only possible but inevitable,"},{"time":399506,"text":"and during a devastating period of relapse"},{"time":401909,"text":"told my terrified family,\n\"Don't give up hope."},{"time":404809,"text":"I believe that Eleanor\ncan get through this."},{"time":407822,"text":"Sometimes, you know, it\nsnows as late as May,"},{"time":410660,"text":"but summer always comes eventually.\""},{"time":414086,"text":"Fourteen minutes is not enough time"},{"time":415940,"text":"to fully credit those\ngood and generous people"},{"time":418876,"text":"who fought with me and for me"},{"time":420853,"text":"and who waited to welcome me back"},{"time":422652,"text":"from that agonized, lonely place."},{"time":425151,"text":"But together, they forged\na blend of courage,"},{"time":427318,"text":"creativity, integrity,\nand an unshakeable belief"},{"time":430904,"text":"that my shattered self could\nbecome healed and whole."},{"time":434753,"text":"I used to say that these people saved me,"},{"time":436730,"text":"but what I now know is they did something"},{"time":438100,"text":"even more important\nin that they empowered me"},{"time":440671,"text":"to save myself,"},{"time":442293,"text":"and crucially, they helped\nme to understand something"},{"time":444841,"text":"which I'd always suspected:"},{"time":446421,"text":"that my voices were a meaningful response"},{"time":448809,"text":"to traumatic life events,\nparticularly childhood events,"},{"time":451759,"text":"and as such were not my enemies"},{"time":453608,"text":"but a source of insight\ninto solvable emotional problems."},{"time":458360,"text":"Now, at first, this was very\ndifficult to believe,"},{"time":461430,"text":"not least because the voices\nappeared so hostile"},{"time":463804,"text":"and menacing, so in this\nrespect, a vital first step"},{"time":467150,"text":"was learning to separate\nout a metaphorical meaning"},{"time":469865,"text":"from what I'd previously\ninterpreted to be a literal truth."},{"time":473643,"text":"So for example, voices\nwhich threatened to attack my home"},{"time":476793,"text":"I learned to interpret\nas my own sense of fear"},{"time":479522,"text":"and insecurity in the world, rather\nthan an actual, objective danger."},{"time":483180,"text":"Now at first, I would have believed them."},{"time":485336,"text":"I remember, for example,\nsitting up one night"},{"time":486908,"text":"on guard outside my parents'\nroom to protect them"},{"time":489378,"text":"from what I thought was a genuine\nthreat from the voices."},{"time":492622,"text":"Because I'd had such a bad\nproblem with self-injury"},{"time":495136,"text":"that most of the cutlery\nin the house had been hidden,"},{"time":497732,"text":"so I ended up arming myself\nwith a plastic fork,"},{"time":500226,"text":"kind of like picnic ware,\nand sort of sat outside the room"},{"time":503012,"text":"clutching it and waiting to spring\ninto action should anything happen."},{"time":506726,"text":"It was like, \"Don't mess with me."},{"time":508398,"text":"I've got a plastic fork, don't you know?\""},{"time":511131,"text":"Strategic."},{"time":512611,"text":"But a later response,\nand much more useful,"},{"time":515217,"text":"would be to try and deconstruct\nthe message behind the words,"},{"time":519635,"text":"so when the voices warned\nme not to leave the house,"},{"time":522657,"text":"then I would thank them\nfor drawing my attention"},{"time":524733,"text":"to how unsafe I felt --"},{"time":525950,"text":"because if I was aware of it, then I could\ndo something positive about it --"},{"time":528843,"text":"but go on to reassure both them and myself"},{"time":531330,"text":"that we were safe and didn't\nneed to feel frightened anymore."},{"time":534829,"text":"I would set boundaries for the voices,"},{"time":536318,"text":"and try to interact with them\nin a way that was assertive"},{"time":539057,"text":"yet respectful,\nestablishing a slow process"},{"time":541313,"text":"of communication and collaboration"},{"time":543669,"text":"in which we could learn to work\ntogether and support one another."},{"time":546968,"text":"Throughout all of this,\nwhat I would ultimately realize"},{"time":549612,"text":"was that each voice was closely related"},{"time":551496,"text":"to aspects of myself,\nand that each of them"},{"time":553805,"text":"carried overwhelming\nemotions that I'd never had"},{"time":556115,"text":"an opportunity to process or resolve,"},{"time":558193,"text":"memories of sexual trauma and abuse,"},{"time":560753,"text":"of anger, shame, guilt, low self-worth."},{"time":563664,"text":"The voices took the place of this pain"},{"time":566164,"text":"and gave words to it,"},{"time":567651,"text":"and possibly one of the greatest\nrevelations"},{"time":569490,"text":"was when I realized that the most hostile\nand aggressive voices"},{"time":572514,"text":"actually represented the parts of me"},{"time":574261,"text":"that had been hurt most profoundly,"},{"time":576474,"text":"and as such, it was these voices"},{"time":578626,"text":"that needed to be shown\nthe greatest compassion and care."},{"time":581968,"text":"It was armed with this\nknowledge that ultimately"},{"time":584983,"text":"I would gather together my shattered self,"},{"time":587271,"text":"each fragment represented\nby a different voice,"},{"time":589886,"text":"gradually withdraw from all my medication,"},{"time":591937,"text":"and return to psychiatry, only this\ntime from the other side."},{"time":596625,"text":"Ten years after the voice first\ncame, I finally graduated,"},{"time":600223,"text":"this time with the highest\ndegree in psychology"},{"time":602117,"text":"the university had ever\ngiven, and one year later,"},{"time":604575,"text":"the highest masters, which shall we say"},{"time":606457,"text":"isn't bad for a madwoman."},{"time":608180,"text":"In fact, one of the voices\nactually dictated the answers"},{"time":610871,"text":"during the exam, which technically\npossibly counts as cheating."},{"time":614101,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":615502,"text":"And to be honest, sometimes I quite\nenjoyed their attention as well."},{"time":618236,"text":"As Oscar Wilde has said,\nthe only thing worse"},{"time":620403,"text":"than being talked about is not\nbeing talked about."},{"time":622920,"text":"It also makes you very\ngood at eavesdropping,"},{"time":625087,"text":"because you can listen\nto two conversations simultaneously."},{"time":627921,"text":"So it's not all bad."},{"time":629210,"text":"I worked in mental health services,"},{"time":630901,"text":"I spoke at conferences,"},{"time":633122,"text":"I published book chapters\nand academic articles,"},{"time":635432,"text":"and I argued, and continue to do so,"},{"time":638222,"text":"the relevance of the following concept:"},{"time":640466,"text":"that an important question in psychiatry"},{"time":642718,"text":"shouldn't be what's wrong with you"},{"time":644362,"text":"but rather what's happened to you."},{"time":646966,"text":"And all the while,\nI listened to my voices,"},{"time":649828,"text":"with whom I'd finally learned\nto live with peace and respect"},{"time":652710,"text":"and which in turn\nreflected a growing sense"},{"time":654828,"text":"of compassion, acceptance\nand respect towards myself."},{"time":658491,"text":"And I remember the most moving\nand extraordinary moment"},{"time":661649,"text":"when supporting another young woman\nwho was terrorized by her voices,"},{"time":664959,"text":"and becoming fully aware,\nfor the very first time,"},{"time":667558,"text":"that I no longer felt that way myself"},{"time":669854,"text":"but was finally able to help\nsomeone else who was."},{"time":673578,"text":"I'm now very proud to be\na part of Intervoice,"},{"time":677146,"text":"the organizational body of the International\nHearing Voices Movement,"},{"time":681115,"text":"an initiative inspired by the work\nof Professor Marius Romme"},{"time":684498,"text":"and Dr. Sandra Escher,"},{"time":685750,"text":"which locates voice hearing\nas a survival strategy,"},{"time":688946,"text":"a sane reaction to insane circumstances,"},{"time":692312,"text":"not as an aberrant symptom\nof schizophrenia to be endured,"},{"time":695971,"text":"but a complex, significant\nand meaningful experience"},{"time":699235,"text":"to be explored."},{"time":701559,"text":"Together, we envisage and enact a society"},{"time":703842,"text":"that understands\nand respects voice hearing,"},{"time":706319,"text":"supports the needs\nof individuals who hear voices,"},{"time":708724,"text":"and which values them as full citizens."},{"time":712005,"text":"This type of society is not only possible,"},{"time":714291,"text":"it's already on its way."},{"time":716303,"text":"To paraphrase Chavez, once\nsocial change begins,"},{"time":720097,"text":"it cannot be reversed."},{"time":722189,"text":"You cannot humiliate\nthe person who feels pride."},{"time":725416,"text":"You cannot oppress the people"},{"time":727207,"text":"who are not afraid anymore."},{"time":729691,"text":"For me, the achievements\nof the Hearing Voices Movement"},{"time":732335,"text":"are a reminder that empathy, fellowship,"},{"time":734769,"text":"justice and respect are more than words;"},{"time":737513,"text":"they are convictions and beliefs,"},{"time":740124,"text":"and that beliefs can change the world."},{"time":742610,"text":"In the last 20 years,\nthe Hearing Voices Movement"},{"time":745385,"text":"has established hearing voices networks"},{"time":747597,"text":"in 26 countries across five continents,"},{"time":750588,"text":"working together to promote\ndignity, solidarity"},{"time":753957,"text":"and empowerment for individuals\nin mental distress,"},{"time":757023,"text":"to create a new language\nand practice of hope,"},{"time":760288,"text":"which, at its very center,\nlies an unshakable belief"},{"time":764232,"text":"in the power of the individual."},{"time":767122,"text":"As Peter Levine has said, the human animal"},{"time":770043,"text":"is a unique being"},{"time":771695,"text":"endowed with an instinctual\ncapacity to heal"},{"time":775069,"text":"and the intellectual spirit\nto harness this innate capacity."},{"time":779280,"text":"In this respect, for members of society,"},{"time":781764,"text":"there is no greater honor or privilege"},{"time":784257,"text":"than facilitating that process\nof healing for someone,"},{"time":786917,"text":"to bear witness, to reach out a hand,"},{"time":789863,"text":"to share the burden\nof someone's suffering,"},{"time":792226,"text":"and to hold the hope for their recovery."},{"time":795300,"text":"And likewise, for survivors\nof distress and adversity,"},{"time":797896,"text":"that we remember we don't\nhave to live our lives"},{"time":800408,"text":"forever defined by the damaging\nthings that have happened to us."},{"time":804120,"text":"We are unique. We are irreplaceable."},{"time":806629,"text":"What lies within us can\nnever be truly colonized,"},{"time":809346,"text":"contorted, or taken away."},{"time":811702,"text":"The light never goes out."},{"time":815800,"text":"As a very wonderful\ndoctor once said to me,"},{"time":817910,"text":"\"Don't tell me what other people\nhave told you about yourself."},{"time":821161,"text":"Tell me about you.\""},{"time":824212,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":826018,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}